Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:27.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}奔向那閃耀的 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:06.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}ふわり、すり抜ける風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:09.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}春の匂いを運び
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:13.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}僕の心をくすぐる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:16.75,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}甘い季節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:22.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}君とつないで歩くこの手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.88,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}かけがえのないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:31.43,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}やさしさの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:40.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}切ない別れに涙あふれた夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:49.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}希望を胸に抱いて…そばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:58.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}舞い散る桜の下で　今、願いを誓うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:05.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}青空にキセキを描いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:09.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}キラメク プリズムの様に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:15.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}恋する素直なほほ笑みで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:20.79,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}サクラアマネクセカイへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:27.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}カガヤク　アシタヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:33.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,285)\fad(800,0)}枯草色的島
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:06.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}忍住眼淚 我笑了笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:12.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}我們今後的去向會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}仰望沒有星星的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:26.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}像許願般深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:32.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}越是想越是無法鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}在那痛楚之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:45.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}喚醒未知的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:55.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}把愛傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:23:03.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}為了明天不被淚水沾濕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:11.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}櫻花飄啊飄 夢之音搖啊搖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:16.09,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}那引導我的溫柔聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:23.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}永遠回響在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:28.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}成為永不枯萎的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:06.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}泣かぬように　笑ってみた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:12.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}僕たちは何処へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}星のない空を見上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:26.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}願うように息をした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:32.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}想うほどにくり返してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}痛みの中で...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:45.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}続く未知を呼び覚ます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:55.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}愛を君に送るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:23:03.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}明日が涙に濡れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:11.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}桜ヒラリ　夢の音ユラリ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:16.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}優しく導く　その声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:23.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}いつまでも心の奥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:28.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}枯れない記憶になる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:40.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,250)\be1\bord2\fad(1600,0)}記憶之淵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.81,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為初音島上重要的旅遊資源的櫻花樹突然間凋零了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:41.65,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為眾人所熟知的賞花名勝 櫻花公園也正如現在大家所見一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此現象現今仍呈現進一步擴散趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.78,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給當地的觀光產業造成了巨大影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:54.21,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天觀光協會早已召開會議擬訂相關對策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.39,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就現在仍處於束手無策的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.26,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並分成了堅持調查櫻花樹凋零原因的解謎派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.71,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及探尋其他可開發利用資源的摸索派兩派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會議曾一度陷入了混亂局面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.35,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於導致櫻花凋零的因果關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.82,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相關部門正從近鄰的居民那裡收集目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:17.38,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十年前曾出現過的不會凋零的櫻花樹也發生過凋零的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.37,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並在十年前左右突然復活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.94,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 這次的這一現象 雖然原因暫時不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:28.16,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過繼續這樣發展下去 初音島上所有的櫻花凋零也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒消失…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實是應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道… 是場夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 凋零了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是造成大騷動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的人們看上很不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經出門了 說是學生會有事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個煎雞蛋真好吃呢 下次也教我怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎雞蛋真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島一直做著的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 義之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬學姐那邊沒問題了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我昨天早退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來真是讓人大吃一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花樹竟突然凋零了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 來學校的路上看到的枯樹也很多呢 總覺得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們已經習慣了盛開的櫻花樹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點孤單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是趁現在盡興地去賞次花什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須解開這一謎團才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫室效應造成的嗎 或者是地磁的顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛 既然凋零了那也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了比起這種事情 我更擔心下節課的數學考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試？什麼考試？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 你忘了嗎？ 今天有數學的隨堂考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這可不行啊 我怎麼這麼粗心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不像雪村的作風啊 你引以為榮的記憶力怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說是一時疏忽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣我的戰友就增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑 現在開始復習也足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣啊 我們一起接受補習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 杏是因為忘了有考試…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是櫻花樹的力量消失了的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 音姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後大哥就火了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我會從大家的記憶中逐漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都將會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後看著弟弟君 也不會記起他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著他也什麼都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不久的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也太殘酷了 弟弟君明明什麼都沒做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯 對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之 今天去哪吃？ 學生食堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 今天我帶了便當…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有答應過你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你個戀愛土豪 真是讓人羡慕啊 好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 學生食堂乃是孤身一人的傢伙們聚集的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然便當就該在外面吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 好像有點冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你好壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也就不會覺得冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做便當給你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 你想謀殺我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會練習的啦 我也想讓你說一次我做的便當很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會是哪年哪月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會進行特訓的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓緊點的話 時間上也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說… 由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 難道我做便當就讓你那麼不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦 我會好好地練習 絕對會讓哥哥你說好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃吧吃吧 開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住慣了的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻小姐消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後誰都不在了…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的話就回答一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是既沒回應 又找不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起 確實抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為懲罰 早飯至少要做3道菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又先出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 奈奈佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 義之君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起 有點發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人是我們班的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 義之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 義之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神不好啊 沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等你哦 櫻內同志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花樹凋零的原因我想過了 想要聽聽你的意見…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的朋友果然還是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別勒那麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出人意料的舉動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你們相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之你 吃了什麼不乾淨的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止弟弟君消失的辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒上課嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的現代國語是寫讀書報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是自修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們去哥哥家裡做火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事要做 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥很寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子 一定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢 莫非你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋 那就我一個人去準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐有空的話也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到別人班裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冒失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人的時候跑到別人的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始問名字了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 有什麼奇怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員終於忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟只試穿不買呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜你一個人試了60套 做得太過火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有60套啦 才58套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 兩個人在購物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼印象呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是我呀 義之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他叫義之 你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是搭訕 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時搭訕兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是想讓一大群可愛女生來侍奉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他找錯人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有事 不能和你約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說還是蠻帥的 有點浪費了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋材料買好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 肉非常便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你負責切菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想讓我一個人做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯頭我會幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 女孩子拿了那麼多東西你沒什麼感覺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開口讓我拿的話會幫你拿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 哥哥 今天肉很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天服務真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的話 你不都是掠奪我精心培育的肉的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 說得真難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天哥哥你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的全都是我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要稍微自重點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是火鍋好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也吃火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天也繼續吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 全火鍋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的一家人的餐桌文化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了吧 還不是只有我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就夠了 雖然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 由夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候說這個雖說有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起的話 會後悔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意和我一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣陪著我 我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然非常高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是兄妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不管發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會在哥哥身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會後悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和往常一樣 和哥哥一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都這樣 和哥哥一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去學校 一起笑啊吵啊吹吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰 你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不認識…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像… 你沒印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是你以前甩掉的男人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 沒有那樣的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過那就是陌生人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了月島 關於吉他手的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了 找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對高達有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要說出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏在心中的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達 給你
