Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:12.08,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}包圍著一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.67,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}相視越久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:24.06,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越會搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:28.24,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想伴你身邊
